videoDetails.title: Texture Review | Blade of Chaos (GoW: Ascension) All 4 Elements Fixed & Optimized [PPSSPP]
videoDetails.shortDescription:
Hello everyone welcome back to another texture review
today im gonna review the Blade of Chaos from GoW: Ascension all 4 Elements but it's Optimized & Fixed cuz i want this texture to look similiar to the original game, i didn't change anything too much i just change the Level 4/Max of Ice of Poseidon and resize all of them to make it a little bit smaller than the Original.
That's it for this video and i hope you like the texture, See You Next Time, BYE~~~
